        <span class="eyebrow">Blog</span>
        <h1>Product Video: How to Turn Features into Sales</h1>
        <p class="lead">Most product videos make the same mistake: they list features. But people don't buy features — they buy what those features let them feel or achieve. A good product film turns specs into desire.</p>
        <p class="post-meta"><span>Viven Team</span> <span>·</span> <span>July 21, 2026</span></p>
      </div>
